{"id":4052,"date":"2025-06-12T17:13:00","date_gmt":"2025-06-12T10:13:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4052"},"modified":"2025-06-12T17:13:00","modified_gmt":"2025-06-12T10:13:00","slug":"dau-tay-trang-han-quoc-gsc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/dau-tay-trang-han-quoc-gsc\/","title":{"rendered":"D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c GSC Natural Makeup Remove"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kho\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da k\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 then ch\u1ed1t. Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang, \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1edbp b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <\/span><\/i><b><i>d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u da l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"danh-gia-tieu-chi-su-dung-dau-tay-trang\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4054\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4054\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4054\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-1.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4054\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dau-tay-trang-cho-tung-loai-da\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang n\u00ean d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t jojoba. Ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t nho s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m ho\u1eb7c trang \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00e0y: N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u. Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n ho\u1eb7c da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n: Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0 xanh. L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quan-tam-den-thanh-phan\"><\/span><strong>Quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm 80% \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua h\u00e0ng, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4056\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4056\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4056\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-3.webp\" alt=\"Quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n\" width=\"800\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-3-300x191.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-3-768x489.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-3-600x382.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4056\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u H\u1ea1t Jojoba, Olive v\u00e0 D\u1ea7u Macadamia: \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 axit b\u00e9o c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho da. Gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t b\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1: V\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, tr\u00e0 xanh gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t nam vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t, d\u1ea7u macca: V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 cao, Vitamin E gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh n\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kha-nang-lam-sach\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho da make up d\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9. D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang khi nh\u0169 ho\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb d\u1ea1ng d\u1ea7u sang d\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa. Gi\u00fap da l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nhanh, s\u1ea1ch, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-gay-bit-tac-da\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc da<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang, c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u kho\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u1eb7ng m\u1eb7t, t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. \u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng d\u00ednh tr\u00ean da s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-goi-y-dau-tay-trang-gsc-natural-makeup-remove-%e2%80%93-sach-sau-va-duong-am-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>\u00a0[G\u1ee3i \u00dd] D\u1ea7u T\u1ea9y Trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove &#8211; S\u1ea1ch S\u00e2u V\u00e0 D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea8m Hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da, D\u1ea7u T\u1ea9y Trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y t\u1eeb GSC, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 da kh\u00f4, da th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trang \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4055\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4055\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4055\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-2.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ea7u T\u1ea9y Trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4055\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u1ea7u T\u1ea9y Trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-nen-chon-dau-tay-trang-gsc\"><\/span><strong><i>T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang GSC?<\/i><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang gsc v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cao c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0: Tinh d\u1ea7u maca, tinh d\u1ea7u Jojoba, Olive gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong gia, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n Isopropyl Myristate gi\u00fap s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb d\u1ea1ng d\u1ea7u sang d\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-nay-giup-gi-cho-ban\"><\/span><strong><i>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap g\u00ec cho b\u1ea1n?<\/i><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nguy\u00ean l\u00fd &#8220;D\u1ea7u h\u00f2a tan d\u1ea7u&#8221;. \u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba s\u00e2u trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp makeup. D\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4057\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4057\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4057\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-4.webp\" alt=\"S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap g\u00ec cho b\u1ea1n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/40-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4057\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap g\u00ec cho b\u1ea1n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da s\u1ea1ch m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i: Sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103ng kh\u00f4.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t Macca, d\u1ea7u Olive, d\u1ea7u Jojoba v\u00e0 b\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1. Cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho da: Sau khi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>D\u1ea7u T\u1ea9y Trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng ai mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 da kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, gi\u00fap gi\u1eef cho da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u da l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang GSC Natural Makeup Remove.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4058,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4052","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-